-------- Angular 1 ---------
1 Controllers and scope   
2 Simple js, no tools     
3 $scope.apply for integration
4 digest everything


-------- Angular 2 ---------
1 Components and directives
2 Typescript transpiler
3 zone.js
4 can set model observable and immutable
server side rendering https://universal.angular.io/